(61, 1, '2011-06-08 19:53:28', '2011-06-09 00:53:28', '<p class="left">We''re here to provide music for your wedding or event. We can get any combination of instrumentalists or vocalists for any type of event. Whether you want a string quartet, bluegrass band, or just a singer and a pianist, we can hook you up! We also offer consultations to help you choose the perfect music for your special day. Our goal is to help you reflect your unique story through the music at your event.</p>\n<p><a href="http://mockingbird.localhost/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/about.jpg"><img src="http://mockingbird.localhost/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/about-300x200.jpg" alt="Chris &amp; Nicki Smallwood" title="Chris &amp; Nicki Smallwood" width="300" height="200" class="alignright size-medium wp-image-62" /></a></p>\n\n<p>We''re husband and wife team of musicians who met and fell in love in Music City. We were both studying music at Belmont. Chris studied piano and Nicki studied voice. It was love at first choir rehearsal!</p>\n<p>With three classical music degrees between us, and with Chris'' experience playing with the Broadway show Rain: <a href="A Tribute to the Beatles</a>, we have the versatility, contacts and experience to bring you the best music in town. Even if we don’t play your event, we hire only the most capable musicians and we will work to make sure your needs are met.</p>\n<p>We love to cook, read, and travel. Chris lives on coffee, Nicki drinks tea. We’re not ashamed to admit that our favorite thing is to sit around and learn new songs together.</p>\n<p>Check out our blog for some listening samples!</p>\n\n', 'Latest News', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '53-autosave', '', '', '2011-06-08 19:53:28', '2011-06-09 00:53:28', '', 53, 'http://mockingbird.localhost/53-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
