(79, 1, '2011-06-08 20:15:32', '2011-06-09 01:15:32', '<h2>Weddinngs</h2>\n<h3>Custom Wedding Ceremony Package</h3>\n<p>Need a gypsy band? Want your brother to sing? Will your wedding be incomplete without a performance of Lady Gaga’s “Bad Romance?” Then you need our custom package! With this package you can customize your wedding by choosing as much or as little as you want. Due to the unique nature of weddings, prices vary, so contact us (link) for a free consultation and quote!</p>\n\n<h3>Basic Wedding Ceremony Package</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>15 minutes prelude music</li>\n<li>60 minutes total contract time</li>\n<li>You choose the prelude style (jazz, classical, pop), but we choose the songs</li>\n<li><a href="">You choose ceremony music from our repertoire</a></li>\n<li>Wedding must take place in the greater</li>\n</ul>\nNashville area\n<ul>\n<li>1 musician- $150</li>\n<li>2 musicians- $250</li>\n<li>3 musicians- $350</li>\n<li>4 musicians- You get the picture…</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Receptions</h3>\n<p>Check out our Events (link) page for your cocktail hour and/or reception.  Check out our blog for some listening samples!</p>\n<h2>Events</h2>\nCustom Event Package From bluegrass bands and string quartets to jazz combos, we can assemble any combination of musicians to suit your needs. It doesn’t matter if it’s a cocktail hour, corporate party, or wedding reception, we can make it happen!\n<p>Because there are so many options, prices vary, so <a href="/contact">contact us</a> for a free consultation and quote!</p>\n<h3>Basic Event Package (Background Music)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>You choose the style (jazz, classical, pop, holiday), but we choose the songs </li>\n<li>$100 per hour, per musician</li>\n<li>Event must take place in the greater Nashville area</li>\n<li>For contracts over one hour, 60 minutes will consist of 55 minutes of music and a 5-minute performer break</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Check out our blog for some listening samples!</p>', 'Information', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '49-autosave', '', '', '2011-06-08 20:15:32', '2011-06-09 01:15:32', '', 49, 'http://mockingbird.localhost/49-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
